<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - The Troll</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'Guardian of the Deep' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/a5_maze-troll.png" alt="Guardian troll encounter">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
    <div class="room-text">
      <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `<p>Yellow, bloodshot eyes fix on you.</p> 
        <p>"HUMAN," it rumbles like grinding rocks. "TURN BACK OR DIE."</p>
        <p>Your enchanted sword gleams. You're armed, prepared. The troll looks slow, brutish. You could take it.</p>
        <p>But then you notice something odd. The troll's eyes aren't entirely hostile. Sad? Tired?</p>
        <p>This creature has been here a long time. Alone.</p>
        <p>The troll raises a massive club, the motion reluctant. "DON'T MAKE TROLL HURT YOU."</p>` %>
          </code>
    </div>

    <hr/>

    <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'Choose your approach:' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/troll-kill"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Attack the troll with your sword' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/troll-nice"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'Lower your weapon and try to talk to the troll' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
